About us







	About us        
    


		     	We are a world-leading provider of sustainable productivity solutions.  Customers benefit from our innovative compressors, vacuum solutions and air treatment systems, construction and mining equipment, power tools and assembly systems.         
		    

























Atlas Copco in brief
 
                	Our solutions include compressors, vacuum solutions, air treatment systems, construction and mining equipment, power tools and assembly systems. 
                

More on Atlas Copco in brief

















Strategy and priorities
 
                	Atlas Copco’s vision is to become and remain First in Mind—First in Choice® with our employees, customers and other stakeholders. 
                

More on Strategy and priorities

















Corporate governance
 
                	Learn more about how we secure long term growth in a decentralized business model. You can also find information about our Annual general Meeting, our Management, our Board of Directors and more. 
                

More on Corporate governance

















Our business
 
                	Our products and services increase customers’ productivity and competitiveness while benefiting society and minimizing the environmental impact.
                

More on Our business

















Our Business Code of Practice
 
                	We create value for all stakeholders
                

More on Our Business Code of Practice

















Innovation
 
                	Innovation drives everything we do. From developing new technologies to revolutionizing productivity, there is always a better way.
                

More on Innovation

















Operational excellence
 
                	We are constantly looking for ways to make our operations more efficient, whether it is connecting our colleagues around the globe, shortening assembly times or improving workplace safety. 
                

More on Operational excellence

















Sustainability
 
                	We take our responsibility towards our customers, the people around us and our planet seriously.
                

More on Sustainability

















Brands
 
                	Atlas Copco has many strong brands driving the success of our business. Find out more about each of our brands here.  
                

More on Brands

















Our history
 
                	Atlas Copco has been driven by an innovative spirit ever since the start in 1873. We have always believed that there is a better way of doing things.
                

More on Our history

















Water for All
 
                	The Water for All non-profit organization is the Atlas Copco Group’s main community engagement project. It is guided by the principle that clean water is a human right and the foundation for better lives.
                

More on Water for All










