Atlas Copco AB





Atlas Copco main office in Nacka (2015)




Type

Public (Aktiebolag)


Traded as
Nasdaq Stockholm: ATCO A, ATCO B


Industry
Industrial equipment


Founded
1873; 144 years ago (1873)


Headquarters
Nacka, Sweden



Key people

Hans Stråberg
(Chairman),
Mats Rahmström
(President and CEO)


Products
Compressors, vacuum solutions, generators, construction and mining equipment, industrial tools and assembly systems


Revenue
SEK 101 billion (2016)



Number of employees

44,695 (2016)


Subsidiaries
Atlas Copco,
